  <brief_title>A Study to Provide Real-world Evidence on the Treatment Goal Achievement Rate, Adherence to and Utilization Patterns of Adalimumab in Patients With Moderate to Severe Plaque Psoriasis in Greece</brief_title>
  <acronym>CONCORDIA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Non-interventional Prospective Cohort Study to Provide Real-world Evidence on the Treatment Goal Achievement Rate, Adherence to and Utilization Patterns of Adalimumab in Patients With Moderate to Severe Plaque Psoriasis in Greece</official_title>
